            Perfect for busy Brentwood families. Weekly or bi-weekly service keeps your home consistently clean so you can focus on family time, not chores.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <li><i class="fas fa-check text-[#FFA985] mr-2"></i>Save up to 20% with weekly service</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check text-[#FFA985] mr-2"></i>Same team learns your preferences</li>
